Images: ["[630_360_16765...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_02/thumb_files/630_360_1676531390-589.jpg)", "[1683469005-14...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_05/1683469005-144.jpg)"]

